title: [Dead Ringer, Showroom]
description: Swathes of black lace adorn the darkly stained wood of this small showroom.  The starry sky is visible through a circular opening in the ceiling, and several candelabra cast their flickering light upon an elegantly carved ebony coffin and a small gilded bell nearby.  A burnt velvet curtain partially obscures a doorway leading to the back of the wagon.
